                      "ep_id": 6,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Eula_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "優菈",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "優菈作為物理輸出的冰屬性大劍角色，與該武器副詞綴",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "物理傷害加成",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "相輔相成，可以很好地發揮該武器的武器效果。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 48,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Razor_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "雷澤",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "作為比較出名的物理輸出大劍角色，雷澤可以突破增加",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "物理傷害加成",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "，這一點與該武器副詞綴相輔相成，使雷澤的B類增傷區優勢更大。武器技能造成的是物理傷害，該傷害同樣可以被",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "物理傷害加成",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "所提高。該武器在四星大劍中是比較適合雷澤的武器，根據具體情況和試作古華會有一些屬性上的細小差距，但差別並不大。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 41,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xinyan_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "辛焱",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "辛焱被大致分個兩種流派，速切大招流和駐場重擊流，後者重擊流在滿命前收益較低，滿命後攜帶白影劍收益則遠遠高於該武器，故該武器比較適合使用速切大招流的物理辛焱，也需要二命至五命。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
